    {
      "bookmarkId": "30883918_5_9216-9257",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9216-9257",
      "markText": "他们的生活资料这样贫乏，所以私有观念不会发达，大酋长位号，无须霸占传给自己的儿子。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30883918&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9216&rangeEnd=9257",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f232f2071d7404e7f2979e?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9216&rangeEnd=9257"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30883918_6_1496-1591",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1496-1591",
      "markText": "这段简单传说，充分证明了与私有财产制度同时并生的、不可分离的是富人荒淫享乐、穷人劳苦受灾、强有力者互相争夺残杀。总而言之，私有制度的发生，是当时社会的大进步，但同时也就带来了人剥削人的灾难。",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30883918&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1496&rangeEnd=1591",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f232f2071d7404e7f2979e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1496&rangeEnd=1591"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30883918_3_415-476",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "415-476",
      "markText": "我们要了解整个人类社会的前途，我们必须了解整个人类社会过去的历史；我们要了解中华民族的前途，我们必须了解中华民族过去的历史",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30883918&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=415&rangeEnd=476",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f232f2071d7404e7f2979e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=415&rangeEnd=476"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30883918_3_1047-1067",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1047-1067",
      "markText": "一言蔽之说，这类书不适于学习历史的需要。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30883918&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1047&rangeEnd=1067",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f232f2071d7404e7f2979e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1047&rangeEnd=1067"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30883918_8_4853-4908",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4853-4908",
      "markText": "封建领主间充满着矛盾，对外紧张，内部自然比较和缓。反之，对外和缓，内部自然紧张起来。所谓“无敌国外患，国恒亡”",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30883918&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4853&rangeEnd=4908",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f232f2071d7404e7f2979e?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4853&rangeEnd=4908"
    },
